title:
BELIB'
1.4.5

creator: Ville de Paris
descriptionHtml:
Belib' is the essential application for all users of the Parisian public network of electric vehicle charging stations!

With the help of Belib' app, you can :
- Find real-time available charge points directly on the map or through a search box, filtered by connector type and power.
- Scan the QR Code on any charge point and start a "Pay As You Go" charge.
- Monitor your ongoing charging session in real-time within the app or through the lock screen widget, stop it with a single click.
- Enable push notifications to be warned when charge stops.
- Create an account and save your mean of payment, get easy access to your charging history and invoices, and set as favorite your preferred charge points for future easy access.
- Use Face / Fingerprint Unlock to connect to the app.
- Subscribe to the Belib' service to benefit from a special rate for all your charges and reserve any available charge point.
- With the help of Android Auto, select a charge point directly on the screen of your car, book it, and use your preferred navigation app to reach it.
descriptionShort: The Parisian public network of charging stations for electric vehicles !

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Charging curve (once charging is complete)
- Improvement of user experience and bug fixes
